  "Name": {
    "English": "EMERGENCY WARP UNIT",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "紧急曲速飞行装置",
    "TraditionalChinese": "緊急空間跳躍裝置"
  },
  "NameLower": {
    "English": "Emergency Warp Unit",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "紧急曲速飞行装置",
    "TraditionalChinese": "緊急空間跳躍裝置"
  },
  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Hyperdrive Augmentation",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "超光速推进器强化",
    "TraditionalChinese": "超空間驅動器擴充"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A significant upgrade to the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Hyperdrive</span> that allows an <span class=\"name name-stellar\">instantaneous warp</span> even while conventional systems are blocked by <span class=\"name name-warning\">starship combat</span>. Access to the emergency warp system is via the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Quick Menu</span>.<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">WARNING:</span> Fast scramble systems mean the user is unable to plot a destination. Uncalculated lightspeed events will damage the unit and require <span class=\"name name-stellar\">frequent repairs</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "能够为<span class=\"name name-technology\">超光速推进器</span>带来显著提升，使得飞船即使是在常规系统因<span class=\"name name-warning\">飞船战斗</span>而被屏蔽的情况下，也能进行<span class=\"name name-stellar\">瞬间曲速飞行</span>。可通过<span class=\"name name-stellar\">快捷菜单</span>打开紧急曲速飞行系统。<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告：</span>快速进入超光速系统意味着用户不能指定目的地。未经计划的光速事件会损坏装置，且推进器需要<span class=\"name name-stellar\">频繁修理</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">超空間驅動器</span>的重大升級，即使傳統系統在<span class=\"name name-warning\">太空船戰鬥</span>遭到阻擋時，還是能進行<span class=\"name name-stellar\">瞬間空間跳躍</span>。可從<span class=\"name name-stellar\">快捷選單</span>使用緊急空間跳躍系統。<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告：</span>快速緊急行動系統代表使用者無法選擇目的地。未經計算的光速活動會損害裝置，需要<span class=\"name name-stellar\">經常維修</span>。"
  },
